                            <label>Розкажіть про себе</label>
                            <textarea id="input-value-autobiography" class="form-control focus-input focus-color-turquoise input-value disabled"  rows="7" data-validation="required" data-validation-error-msg-required="Це обов'язкове поле" disabled readonly>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla audantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae
